# 🏆 HolyClub Esports Analytics

A data analytics project built on top of a real-world esports platform database.

This project explores competitive matchmaking, player performance, ranking systems, platform operations and user behavior using SQL, Python, MySQL and Business Intelligence concepts.

The objective is to transform operational data into actionable insights, KPIs and dashboards that support data-driven decision-making within the HolyClub ecosystem.

---

# 🎮 About HolyClub

HolyClub is a competitive Counter-Strike 2 platform that provides:

* Competitive Matchmaking
* Championships and Tournaments
* ELO Ranking System
* HolyCoins Economy
* Community Features
* Support and Moderation Systems
* Anti-Cheat and Fair Play Monitoring

This project uses real production data to perform analytical exploration and business intelligence initiatives.

