# 📊 Analytics Modules

## Player Analytics

* Top Killers
* MVP Ranking
* K/D Ratio
* Average Rating
* Matches Played
* ELO Analytics

## Match Analytics

* Match Completion Rate
* Match Cancellation Rate
* Match Status Distribution
* Average Match Duration
* Average Map Duration

## Map Analytics

* Most Played Maps
* Kills by Map
* Average Rating by Map
* Average K/D by Map

## Infrastructure Analytics

* Match Distribution by Server
* Platform Usage Metrics

---

# 📁 Insights Repository

Analytical findings and business observations are documented separately inside the `insights/` directory.

Current reports:

* Player Analytics Insights
* Match Analytics Insights
* Map Analytics Insights
* ELO Analytics Insights

This separation allows the repository to distinguish analytical logic (queries and scripts) from business conclusions (insights).

